These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, juice, fanta, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Beverage   | fanta | juice | water | hot-chocolate |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different games are played: chess, backgammon, billiard, snooker
1. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1
2. the person playing chess is on the far left##1
3. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Game   | chess | billiard | backgammon | snooker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, entrepreneur, writer, analyst
1. the writer is on the left of the journalist##1
2. the entrepreneur is on the left of the analyst##1
3. the entrepreneur is on the right of the journalist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Job   | writer | journalist | entrepreneur | analyst |

