.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-4::.
4 different pets are kept: goat, cat, horse, lizard
1. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the lizard is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |    3    |  4  |
| Pet   | horse | goat | cat | lizard |

