.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-10::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, blend, fonseca, bluemaster
1. the blend-smoker is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
2. the fonseca-smoker is on the far right##1
3. the bluemaster-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |  2   |  3  |  4  |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | pall-mall | blend | fonseca |

